data.title: Killsadie
data.text:
Killsadie broke up in the Fall of 2001. Members continue playing music in Pretty Girls Make Graves, Minus the Bear, Sharks Keep Moving, On Alaska, and a few other bands.

Members:

Erin Tate – drums (Spring 1997-Fall 2001)

Jay Clark – guitar (Summer 1997-Fall 2001)

Little Steve – vocals (February 1998-Fall 2001)

Patrick Scott – guitar/vocals (Fall 99-Fall 2001)

Corey – bass (Winter 2001-Fall 2001)

Rebecca – keyboard (Summer 2001-Fall 2001)

B.J. Woulett – guitar (Winter 1998-Fall 1999)

Bob Eisenbich – bass (Spring 1997-Fall 2000)

Josh VanLoon – vocals (January 1997-Winter 1998)

Jason Aaronen – vocals (Spring 1997-Fall 1997)

Erik Hanson – guitar (Spring 1997-Summer 1997)

Knol Tate – guitar (Spring 1997-December 1998)
